title: PM Sheikh Hasina urges for implementing Dhaka-Chittagong Express Railway (Bangladesh Awami League)
text: ( Source : Bangladesh Awami League ) Published on Thursday, 08 October 2015 11:32 Hits: 5 Prime Minister Sheikh Hasina today asked the authorities concerned to implement Dhaka-Chittagong Expressway and Dhaka-Chittagong Express Railway projects
